    {
        "url": "/quotes/wietse_venema_333649",
        "quote": "In a previous life I wrote the software that controlled my physics experiments. That software had to deal with all kinds of possible failures in equipment. That is probably where I learned to rely on multiple safety nets inside and around my systems.",
